### expected behaviour
the server should notice when a user wants to restore a folder that its name is currently in use

### actual behaviour
empty screen

### steps to reproduce
1. create a folder called it test
2. select to delete this folder
3. create again another folder called test and upload something to this folder
4 go to the trash 
5. select to restore the test folder
6. after that it is not possible to connect to the server.

### server configuration
acceptance-testing master_on_apache_with_sqlite
